window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>On September 28th, a geologist working in Death Valley finds a mysterious new cinder cone in very well-mapped area. On October 1, the government of Australia announces the discovery of an enormous granite mountain. Like the cinder cone, it wasn't there six months ago. </p> <p>Something is happening to planet Earth, and the truth is too terrifying to contemplate.</p>"; 
